  "title": "Principal Technical Recruiter – Emerging Technologies",
  "description": "<p>Regional Principal Technical Recruiter (Singapore) — P&L Responsibility</p><p>About the role:<br />We’re looking for a senior Regional Technical Recruiter to lead cross‑border technical hiring for our clients across Southeast Asia with a primary focus on Singapore. This is a regional role with P&L accountability for your division within the Singapore business and commercial responsibility for recruitment outcomes across the region.</p><p>Key responsibilities</p><ul><li>Lead regional technical recruitment across Southeast Asia for high‑growth technology clients.  </li><li>Own end‑to‑end hiring strategy for hard‑to‑fill roles (AI, data, software engineering, product).  </li><li>Partner directly with founders, CTOs and regional hiring managers on workforce planning and hiring prioritisation.  </li><li>Drive revenue‑linked recruitment outcomes, including retained and exclusive search mandates.  </li><li>Build and manage cross‑border candidate pipelines across multiple markets.  </li><li>Represent the firm in regional talent advisory, employer branding and client engagement initiatives.  </li><li>Operate with high autonomy and accountability for hiring outcomes, client satisfaction and financial performance (P&L management for Singapore).</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Proven experience in regional / cross‑border technical recruitment across SEA.  </li><li>Strong exposure to technology and emerging‑tech roles (AI, data science, software engineering, product).  </li><li>Track record of delivering revenue‑driven hiring outcomes (retained/exclusive mandates).  </li><li>Comfortable operating independently in a senior individual‑contributor capacity.  </li><li>Experience working with senior stakeholders and decision‑makers (founders, CTOs).  </li><li>Commercial acumen and experience or willingness to take on P&L responsibility.</li></ul><p>What we offer</p><ul><li>Regional remit with opportunity to shape market strategy and scale business.  </li><li>Competitive base + performance incentives tied to revenue and margin. Uncapped commission. Equity/long‑term incentives may be available.  </li><li>Flexible/hybrid working and budget for professional development.  </li><li>Supportive, founder‑led environment and strong market network.</li></ul>",
